WEBVTT

00:02.070 --> 00:03.437
Why are you acting so weird?

00:03.570 --> 00:05.820
Nicole says it's because I like you.

00:07.851 --> 00:10.110
- Don't you like me?
- Yeah, I do.

00:10.390 --> 00:12.204
My dad was notorious
for breaking promises.

00:12.324 --> 00:13.736
Don't wanna be that kind of father.

00:13.856 --> 00:15.758
You're not; you're a great father.

00:15.959 --> 00:17.042
My sister Jessi,

00:17.206 --> 00:18.731
she's been having some problems.

00:18.851 --> 00:20.622
We hope you might sit down with her.

00:20.742 --> 00:22.382
It's a really pretty necklace.

00:22.669 --> 00:25.067
Thanks. It's a remnant
from my Declan days.

00:26.769 --> 00:29.826
- Jessi, we're leaving.
- You can't tell me what to do!

00:34.074 --> 00:35.080
Foss!

00:38.774 --> 00:41.091
- I want to tell you everything.
- I'm ready to hear it.

00:43.458 --> 00:44.465
Foss did this?

00:46.000 --> 00:52.074
